&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;In order to prevent such accidents in the future the following measures
were taken:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul type="disc"&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;Performance of the risk
     analysis for the job positions where substances and mixtures dangerous to
     health are used or stored;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;Equipment of the
     employees with personal toxic meters (for monitoring toxic atmosphere);&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;Introduction of the stationary
     safety sensors (explosimeters, analysers) into the control system;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;Training of the
     employees in order to increase awareness on the dangers connected with
     work on the installations using dangerous substances;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;Revision of the
     procedures on very dangerous works;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;Strengthen of the
