&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;There were measurements of the carbon monoxide concentration taken in
the vicinity of half-combustion installation. There was an increase of the
concentration (over the highest acceptable concentration) of a substance
observed. The plant initiated its chemical alert procedure.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;The following immediate measures were taken:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style="margin-top: 0cm;" type="circle"&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;evacuation
     of the people from the area of compression room;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;abortion of
     the start up process at half-combustion low-pressure installation;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal" style=""&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;searching
     for the emission source of carbon monoxide.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;Medical service attended the accident.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

